snippet.title: Harry Potter: Magic Awakened Quidditch Ground
snippet.description:
As Madam Hooch would say, "I want a nice clean game, from all of you." 

Hear the roaring crowds of Hogwarts, students and teachers alike, as you step out onto the pitch. Mount your brooms and get ready to play Quidditch, in Harry Potter: Magic Awakened. 

#HarryPotter #MagicAwakened

FACEBOOK - https://www.facebook.com/Harry-Potter-Magic-Awakened-105465481625348/
TWITTER - https://twitter.com/HarryPotterMAEN
WEBSITE - https://www.harrypottermagicawakened.com/global/
